Class DurationPickerPopup

java.lang.Object
javafx.stage.Window
javafx.stage.PopupWindow
javafx.scene.control.PopupControl
com.dlsc.gemsfx.skins.DurationPickerPopup
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable
public class DurationPickerPopup extends javafx.scene.control.PopupControl
This popup is used by the TimePicker control to let the user select a time via mouse or touch.
